body_html:
a = [np.arange(3), np.arange(5)]
dataset = tf.contrib.data.Dataset.from_generator(lambda: a, tf.int64)
ds1=dataset.repeat(10)
value = ds1.make_one_shot_iterator().get_next()
sess.run(value) /// first element
sess.run(value) /// second element
sess.run(value) // Out of range message
`

throws OutOfRangeError : End of sequence
